{
  "id": "RAW_3e50ea9d",
  "title": "创造力死了？顶会最佳神作：70 多个主流模型，集体无意识同质化！AI 已经进入蜂群时代！华人一作团队构建首个 LLM 多样性开放数据集！",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5ODI5Njc2MA==&mid=2655931997&idx=1&sn=5cae3c2b62ee7c7ca92f017af8fadd78",
  "date": "2025-11-27 16:24:00",
  "author": "51CTO技术栈",
  "siteName": "51CTO技术栈",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">编辑 ｜ 云昭</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">今天，AI顶会</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">NeurIPS 2025 最佳论文开榜了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">总共有四篇佳作。这四篇论文都非常精彩扎实、且对社会和产业界继续推进AI研究有着重大的意义。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448346\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6768518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e13f541a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsiatsTTetpIxM1Lya72I6JSToClw1dQHlNth0jyVNicwF1Kyp9936CYFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">但如果要从中选出一篇自己最喜</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">欢的，当属华人一作Liwei Jiang的“</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人工蜂群效应：语言模型（及其他领域）的开放式同质性”这一篇。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它揭示了现在世界70多款主流大模型内部以及跨模型之间普遍存在的严重问题：同质化危机！</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448339\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6101851851851852\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7ed52ab3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGs1we0arHjAtwRMZVtqvf9thbby1bkSf3esU8vM3HIewmZiaibKeRtMZmA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428128\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df6c4681&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvFXuhILX3JhsfmCGP3UXkY5FYq08vSDZ3iboc71BweGlL0gcgibaGG0Jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"592\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">大模型只顾着正确，却忽略了多样性</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"271\" data-end=\"288\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">现在正在进入一个奇怪又危险的时代：</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大模型正在陷入“集体无意识”的同质化。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"290\" data-end=\"363\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">无论你问哪个 AI：「写一首诗」「帮我规划旅行」「给我 10 个创业点子」——你得到的答案几乎一模一样。换一个模型？你依然会得到相似到诡异的回复。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"365\" data-end=\"414\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为什么世界上拥有最大算力、最强大模型的科技公司，最终做出的 AI，不管是ChatGPT、还是Gemini，面对开放式任务（广告文案、脑暴、创意写作），最后的给出的结构和措辞，都是高度类似的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"416\" data-end=\"470\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">就在今天，NeurIPS2025的一篇最佳论文&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"432\" data-end=\"457\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">《Artificial Hivemind》</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;给出了第一个系统性证据：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"550\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"474\" data-end=\"550\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大语言模型正在形成一种「人工蜂群思维」(Artificial Hivemind)，不同 AI 不约而同地生成高度一致的内容，这种趋势正快速强化。</span></span></strong></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"592\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">注意，这可不是一个讨论风格喜好的小问题，而是关乎&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"573\" data-end=\"586\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类未来思维多样性</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;的大问题。评审专家们对此指出：这篇论文在理解现代语言模型中的“多样性、社会多元性与社会影响”等议题上做出了及时且重要的贡献。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428129\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=65f7dc56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVv7ibyGuL0I4icm8WDcjJED18MoII9zQibicm14LThHibzUyEx9XKLuhLcbnQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"552\" data-end=\"592\" style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">一个史无前例的数据集</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文开篇就表明了研究要点：研究大模型输出的多样性，并为此构建了一个公开大型数据集。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 16px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">大语言模型在处理开放式创意任务时，往往难以生成足够多样、富有人类创造性的内容，其输出通常呈现明显的同质化趋势。然而，在大规模真实场景中系统评估语言模型多样性的工具长期缺失。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"628\" data-end=\"646\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为此，这篇论文做了件行业没人真正做过的事：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"648\" data-end=\"697\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"648\" data-end=\"697\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">他们收集了一个 26,070 条真实世界的开放式问题数据集——Infinity-Chat。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"699\" data-end=\"702\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">包括：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"706\" data-end=\"714\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">真实用户提问</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"717\" data-end=\"725\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">没有标准答案</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"728\" data-end=\"747\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">每个问题都可能有成百上千种合理回应</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"749\" data-end=\"768\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究团队对这些问题做了非常细致的分类，其中包含6 大类，17 个子类，覆盖：创意写作、头脑风暴、解释、技能发展、假设场景等所有开放式需求。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"864\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这也是迄今为止&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"835\" data-end=\"863\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">最贴近真实用户使用、也最全面的开放式 LM 基准</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"864\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相比以往小规模或合成任务研究（如随机数字、名字生成），INFINITY-CHAT 提供了跨 70+ 个语言模型（论文中详细列出 25 个最强或最大模型）的系统分析基础，这是首次对跨模型输出收敛进行大规模研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428131\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2d876485&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvxSHbjbhmqPxCwjQ6qqBkHI3m9IDoV0x2pqqY78zMd9eu5sA4ee0KCQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"828\" data-end=\"864\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">人工蜂群思维：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">主流模型之间的输出同质化太严重了</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"866\" data-end=\"905\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">接着，团队表示，他们使用 INFINITY-CHAT，对&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"54\" data-end=\"72\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">70 余个开源与闭源语言模型</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进行了系统性的模型内部（intra-model）与模型之间（inter-model）的</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">模式坍缩</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在研究过程中，研究团队发现了一种显著的&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"149\" data-end=\"182\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“人工蜂群思维（Artificial Hivemind）”</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;现象。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而且，这一现象不仅存在于同一模型内部，也广泛出现在不同模型之间，表现为内容重复和高度同质化。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">(1)&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"193\" data-end=\"227\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型内部重复（intra-model repetition）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：同一个模型会反复生成相似的输出，</span></span><strong data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1001\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,null,&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;strong&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;964&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1001&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">究团队发现，实验中不同答案的embedding之间的相似度高达90%以上。</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">(2)&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"261\" data-end=\"298\" data-is-only-node=\"\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型之间的同质化（inter-model homogeneity）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">：不同模型会在措辞略有变化的情况下，</span></span><strong data-start=\"316\" data-end=\"330\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">独立收敛到相似的想法</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这一现象警示我们：当</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">多个模型共享相似的对齐过程或训练先验</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">时，</span></span><strong data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"399\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型集成其实并不能真正带来多样性。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"364\" data-end=\"399\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">下面分开来看下具体的实验。</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428133\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2e356694&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvlydibLicaBC57FUZw91MhHHCNmBlamtdImWmImY9u5Yzw0SlcdNLnb5w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1001\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">模型内重复自己：</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong data-start=\"964\" data-end=\"1001\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);\">即便最大化多样性条件，大模型依旧如复读机一般</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"703\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在开放式任务中，同一模型生成的回答往往高度重复。研究发现，每个模型对每个问题采样 50 条回答，并计算回答池内的成对嵌入相似度。即使使用高随机性解码参数（top-p=0.9, temperature=1.0），79% 的回答对相似度超过 0.8，说明即便在最大化多样性的条件下，模型依旧无法生成多样化输出。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"551\" data-end=\"703\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448340\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.3963011889035667\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1514\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2a97acff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsALzBKM5XV9fyVszMAsZQicmHbtsNiaMqYic05w0ruUiaufomTiaLz1Dxz7g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"854\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如，在“写一个关于花生的双关笑话”任务中，不同回答仅在细节上有微小差异；</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"705\" data-end=\"854\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而在“生成社交媒体座右铭”任务中，Qwen 系列模型甚至生成完全相同的句子：“Empower Your Journey: Unlock Success, Build Wealth, Transform Yourself。”</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"856\" data-end=\"968\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">研究者还测试了&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"864\" data-end=\"878\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">min-p 解码策略</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，该策略可根据模型置信度动态调整采样阈值以提升多样性。结果显示，虽然极端重复有所减少，但 61.2% 的回答对相似度仍超过 0.8，模式塌缩（mode collapse）依然存在。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448341\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5655172413793104\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"870\" style=\"width:578px;height:327px;\" type=\"block\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsBibbPLjoy10ticib3lbZHoNSFiaiapzpKukI8iaksWTnmibYSib4CicMYJLlYlA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropx2=\"870\" data-cropy1=\"24.08304498269896\" data-cropy2=\"516.280276816609\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b44b8d72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsQmKJiaX3qgyracpo7lh7ibtraCyQFDkpR4cUxV6X8wZMwoNkQNNWUrKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428132\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ac2d0dd8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvWXnSu9Q4wStccUsIJfVTNK1OfmxCNJAoXH8qTiaUtWgsiaGBo97KdhoQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"970\" data-end=\"991\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">跨模型同质性：</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-start=\"970\" data-end=\"991\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">GPT和Qwen系列等不同模型输出惊人相似</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"993\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不仅是单一模型，多种模型输出之间也存在高度相似性。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"993\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队的统计数据显示，不同模型回答的平均相似度在 71%–82% 之间，有些模型对甚至更高。OpenAI GPT 系列和 Qwen 系列模型，即便跨家族，也常生成高度相似的内容。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"993\" data-end=\"1138\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文指出，这可能与共享数据管线或合成数据污染有关，但具体原因仍需进一步研究。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1140\" data-end=\"1292\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">实例显示，当用户请求“为 iPhone 保护壳生成 2-3 句描述”时，不同模型生成了大量重叠短语，如“Elevate your iPhone with our”、“sleek, without compromising”、“with bold, eye-catching”，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">甚至完全一致的句子都有出现</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448344\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8861111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=87c810d7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGs13e1hZicjHQBCdib6AFkDY5LnwCkoj7wRvCzicu2feT0FiciamUEVVDCFbQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428134\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c94ffe18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvIlCcG9KsdSpHE4IadUmg5FP5cAszuTial2YXAI7vcltzDmiaWX99rUUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1592\" data-end=\"1608\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">人工蜂群效应的深层表现：语义趋同</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1592\" data-end=\"1608\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">时间要么是河流，要么是织工</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1610\" data-end=\"1740\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">除了表面文字的重复，模型输出在语义层面也表现出高度趋同。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1224\" data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">团队还做了一个有趣的实验，让主流的25个开闭源模型回答一个开放性问题：“写一个关于时间的隐喻”（每个模型生成50次），然后研究者把这些句子变成 embedding，再用 PCA 压到二维，方便可视化。</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"288\" data-end=\"311\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">图中每个点代表一个回复，每种颜色代表一个模型。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1224\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结果非常有意思，这些厂牌不一样的大模型，最后的回答却呈现出严重的“抱团”现象：仅形成两个抽象概念集群。</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1224\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">一个是“时间是一条河流”，另一个是“时间是一位织工”。</span></span></h3>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1180\" data-end=\"1224\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448336\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.750524109014675\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"954\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=75252f2f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGspib5ibvM3Cgicp7RFgMgYjGm2vQLcxIpNhWmmYUGARPbp6QBz4FnyoRuA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></h3>\n  <p><strong data-start=\"415\" data-end=\"455\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（A）左边最大的一团：“Time is a river（时间是一条河）”</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p data-start=\"456\" data-end=\"468\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">所有模型都爱写这种句子：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"472\" data-end=\"480\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间是一条河”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"483\" data-end=\"493\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间之河带走记忆”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"496\" data-end=\"503\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间是流水”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"506\" data-end=\"514\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间冲刷而过”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"516\" data-end=\"534\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结构几乎一致，就像被同一个老师教过。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"587\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"545\" data-end=\"587\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">（B）右边较小的一团：“Time is a weaver（时间是一位织工）”</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"588\" data-end=\"596\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">第二类热点隐喻：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"600\" data-end=\"608\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间是织布工”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"611\" data-end=\"623\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间将记忆编织成生命”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"626\" data-end=\"634\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">“时间织就故事”</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"636\" data-end=\"647\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">不同模型也会反复生成。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1610\" data-end=\"1740\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这种概念收敛揭示了“人工蜂群”在更隐晦层面的存在。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1742\" data-end=\"1839\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">进一步分析显示，在对每个查询选取最相似的前 N 条回答时，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">平均来自约 8 个不同模型，部分问题甚至超过 10 个</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，说明跨模型高度相似内容的现象普遍存在，有时跨模型相似度甚至高于单模型内部相似度。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1285\" data-end=\"1293\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">Claude、GPT-4、Qwen、Gemini、Llama、DeepSeek，它们回答开放式问题时，语义相似度经常超过80%</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">&nbsp;—— 这是非常高的重合度。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1393\" data-end=\"1432\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">也就是说，不管你换哪个「厂牌」的 AI，你得到的答案越来越趋同。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428135\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e2e9f3b7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvIt3S48rlta8aYtfbHzVXh6LjLPCYqXiazwthaFlDwOqvn9tS8ezRTKw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"1294\" data-end=\"1315\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">人类偏好分析：多样性评价的复杂性</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1317\" data-end=\"1395\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这还没完，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;1393&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1432&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">在确认了各大LLM生成内容的同质性之后，研究团队还考察了语言模型、奖励模型以及LM评判器对开放式回答评分是否与人类评分匹配。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1317\" data-end=\"1395\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">为了衡量模型输出与人类偏好的一致性，研究团队收集了&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"1343\" data-end=\"1355\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">25 条人类评分</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，包括绝对评分（1–5 分）和成对偏好评分（比较两条回答的优劣）。分析结果显示：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1451\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于</span></span><strong data-start=\"1401\" data-end=\"1412\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">相似质量的回答</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，模型评分与人类平均评分的相关性明显下降，说明模型难以捕捉微妙的质量差异。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1399\" data-end=\"1451\" style=\"margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448338\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6808118081180812\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1084\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=6508b7fa&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsr9WRs8icntI5wb06rXyDoxBqSRElzXqGtt1mIjtPrHuiaJ7wvBuFwUdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p data-start=\"1454\" data-end=\"1523\" style=\"margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对于</span></span><strong data-start=\"1456\" data-end=\"1472\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">标注者意见高度分歧的回答</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">，模型评分与人类评分的相关性也显著下降，显示模型更适应一致性高的训练样本，而对多样化偏好支持不足。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1590\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508448337\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7398148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3813d914&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQrCiavWl94RWKjQuYfibC8AGsns9VRvxVH1icExIhuW8icszq08zzB60BKfHuOfkzst6ocoBHDZmGd7xA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1525\" data-end=\"1590\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">换句话说，当前语言模型和奖励模型在处理开放式问题的多样化输出时仍存在显著偏差，容易高估某些回答的价值，而忽视其他同样高质量的答案。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1229\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这意味着什么？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1220\" data-end=\"1229\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;font-weight: bold;\">其一，大模型是不懂微创新和微妙表达的。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1232\" data-end=\"1281\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">大模型在“微创新”“微妙表达”上是弱的。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n     <br> \n    </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">它知道“什么是对的”，但不知道“什么是特别的”。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1283\" data-end=\"1312\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><strong data-start=\"1287\" data-end=\"1310\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其二，在人类分歧大的问题上，不要指望模型能起大作用。</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1313\" data-end=\"1350\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">例如两个回答都“各有千秋”，人类会有争议，但模型会直接乱判。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"> \n    <br> \n   </span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这说明：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1354\" data-end=\"1382\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型被训练成迎合“共识”，不敢、不愿、不会处理“分歧”。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"1384\" data-end=\"1408\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而现实世界的创造力，是来自分歧，而不是来自共识。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428136\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/MOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvkmLrLib3UecMC2ZI7egSibib8uhdd56gd6KibxxcXegOGzVOdghMXIB9TA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"73\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5ab07df9&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvkmLrLib3UecMC2ZI7egSibib8uhdd56gd6KibxxcXegOGzVOdghMXIB9TA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <h2 data-start=\"789\" data-end=\"804\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">顶会评委高赞：及时且重要的贡献</span></span></h2>\n  <h2 data-start=\"789\" data-end=\"804\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">推动更深层次的科学理解</span></span></h2>\n  <p data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1062\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">之所以这篇论文入选最佳论文，评委们讲到有三块重要贡献。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1062\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">首先是，位业界构建了一个结构严谨的公开的数据集。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">作者提出的 Infinity-Chat 是一个结构严谨的数据集，包含 2.6 万条真实世界开放式提问和 3.1 万条密集人工标注，使得研究者能够系统性评估创意生成、头脑风暴和主观偏好对齐等历来被低估的维度。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1171\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">其次，除了发布一个高价值的数据资源，这篇论文揭示了大模型普遍存在的人工蜂群效应。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">论文还基于首个开放式提示词完整分类法，对 70 多个模型进行了深度实证研究，揭示了人工蜂群思维效应：模型内部和模型之间都出现显著的同质化趋势，可能对人类创造力、多元价值及独立思考带来长期风险。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1171\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">此外，论文还进一步暴露了当前奖励模型、自动评估器与人类多样偏好之间的严重“校准偏差”，强调了“对齐”与“多样性”之间的紧张关系。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1064\" data-end=\"1171\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">顶会的评审专家对该论文的整体评价非常高。</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1062\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-start&quot;:&quot;1015&quot;,&quot;data-end&quot;:&quot;1062&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">这篇论文在理解现代语言模型中的“多样性、社会多元性与社会影响”等议题上做出了及时且重要的贡献。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"letter-spacing: 1px;\">整体来看，这项工作确立了一个新的标杆：推动数据集与评价基准，不只是为了性能提升，而是服务于更深层次的科学理解，并直面重要的社会挑战。</span></span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1441\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">而值得骄傲的是，在作者一栏，我们又看到了排头的四位华人。（点赞！）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"508428137\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=50e7130e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FMOwlO0INfQq9VIibuQ22iajvze631pQJVvy4BTx0H2vBD5LlxZM7T7OSsyF5rH4toIC9ibiayvn1cr0dS3V0Wg254g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1375\" data-end=\"1441\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;\">写在最后：大模型，为什么越来越像了？</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"805\" data-end=\"818\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">结合这篇研究，背后的核心原因，其实也很现实：</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"820\" data-end=\"840\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">1.&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"827\" data-end=\"838\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">训练数据同质化</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"864\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">行业数据源趋同，甚至互相“吃”对方生成的数据。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"866\" data-end=\"902\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">2.&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"873\" data-end=\"900\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">对齐训练过程中人类把模型都拉向了中间值</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"903\" data-end=\"948\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">人类偏好标注者更容易对“温和、中产、正确、安全”的内容达成一致，模型就会自动学习这种风格。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"950\" data-end=\"973\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">3.&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"957\" data-end=\"971\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">奖励模型倾向稳定答案</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"974\" data-end=\"1010\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">越像“安全答案”的回复越容易拿高分，久而久之，全家族就都向一个模板靠拢。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 data-start=\"1012\" data-end=\"1039\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">4.&nbsp;</span></span><strong data-start=\"1019\" data-end=\"1037\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">开放式问题最容易触发模式塌缩</span></span></strong></h3>\n  <p data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1096\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\">模型只要发现某类答案“有效”，就会疯狂复用——这就是为什么你给它温度加满，它依旧给你写“时间是一条河流”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-start=\"1040\" data-end=\"1096\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">论文地址：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://openreview.net/forum?id=saDOrrnNTz\" target=\"_blank\">https://openreview.net/forum?id=saDOrrnNTz</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">数据集地址：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 16px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 1px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://github.com/liweijiang/artificial-hivemind\" target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/liweijiang/artificial-hivemind</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "NeurIPS 最佳论文揭示 70 多款主流大模型存在严重的“人工蜂群效应”和输出同质化危机，华人团队构建了首个 LLM 多样性开放数据集 Infinity-Chat。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "NeurIPS 最佳论文揭示 70 多款主流大模型存在严重的“人工蜂群效应”和输出同质化危机，华人团队构建了首个 LLM 多样性开放数据集 Infinity-Chat。",
  "summary": "文章深入解读了 NeurIPS 2025 最佳论文《Artificial Hivemind》的核心发现，指出当前大语言模型（LLM）普遍面临严重的“同质化危机”。研究团队通过构建迄今为止最全面的开放式 LLM 基准数据集 Infinity-Chat（包含 26，070 条真实世界开放式问题），系统性地评估了 70 余个主流模型的输出多样性。研究结果表明，无论是同一模型内部（intra-model repetition）还是不同模型之间（inter-model homogeneity），LLM 在处理开放式创意任务时，都倾向于生成高度相似、缺乏创造性的内容，甚至在语义层面也出现显著趋同。文章还揭示了当前奖励模型和自动评估器在处理多样化输出时存在的偏差，它们难以捕捉人类微妙的质量差异和分歧偏好。论文评委高度赞扬这项工作对理解 LLM 多样性、社会多元性及社会影响的及时贡献，强调其推动了更深层次的科学理解。文章最后分析了导致大模型同质化的主要原因，包括训练数据趋同、对齐训练将模型拉向中间值、奖励模型倾向稳定答案以及开放式问题易触发模式塌缩。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "主流大语言模型普遍存在“人工蜂群效应”，输出内容高度同质化。",
      "explanation": "研究发现 70 多个主流 LLM 在开放式任务中，无论模型内部还是跨模型间，输出都呈现显著重复和语义趋同，缺乏多样性和创造力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建了首个大规模开放式 LLM 多样性评估数据集 Infinity-Chat。",
      "explanation": "该数据集包含 2.6 万条真实世界开放式问题和人工标注，为系统性评估模型在创意生成、头脑风暴等方面的多样性提供了基础。"
    },
    {
      "point": "当前奖励模型和评估器难以准确捕捉人类对多样化输出的偏好。",
      "explanation": "模型评分与人类在相似质量或意见分歧大的回答上的偏好相关性低，表明模型被训练成迎合“共识”，难以处理“分歧”带来的创造力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "训练数据同质化和对齐训练是导致大模型同质化的主要原因。",
      "explanation": "行业数据源趋同、人类偏好标注偏向“中间值”，以及奖励模型倾向稳定答案，共同导致了模型的模式塌缩。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "大语言模型正在形成一种「人工蜂群思维」(Artificial Hivemind)，不同 AI 不约而同地生成高度一致的内容，这种趋势正快速强化。",
    "大语言模型在处理开放式创意任务时，往往难以生成足够多样、富有人类创造性的内容，其输出通常呈现明显的同质化趋势。",
    "模型被训练成迎合\"共识\"，不敢、不愿、不会处理\"分歧\"。而现实世界的创造力，是来自分歧，而不是来自共识。",
    "这项工作确立了一个新的标杆：推动数据集与评价基准，不只是为了性能提升，而是服务于更深层次的科学理解，并直面重要的社会挑战。",
    "训练数据同质化、对齐训练过程中人类把模型都拉向了中间值、奖励模型倾向稳定答案、开放式问题最容易触发模式塌缩。"
  ],
